- Some Workers and Pages projects would not load in dash, showing an "Internal Error" page
- Not all custom domains showed up for a Worker
- Users could not change the git branch in their Pages project environment

The duration of this impact was from September, 19th 16:45  UTC through September, 20th 18:45 UTC.

No production traffic to Workers or Pages was affected. Workers and Pages APIs were also not affected.
